                                "byte_start": 85390,
                                "byte_stop": 111303,
                                "text": "The opinion of the Court in two cases will be announced by Justice Thomas."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 6.471,
                        "stop": 147.566,
                        "byte_start": 111303,
